{"tid":619161,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"原來m記而家仲有全鎚","createTime":"2018-04-06T11:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T12:28:22.000Z","uid":3146,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a814659752f8317ebaacb413a3107d4a9326b654","tid":619161,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/193608_04afd7ae1a85118001338ff957e82396.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F193608_04afd7ae1a85118001338ff957e82396.png&h=7b6240bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從m記無得叫全翼之後都無再食雞翼<br />\n今日突然好想食 就叫左兩隻黎食下<br />\n叫埋右 屌你老母肥絲大隻<br />\n諗住有隻翼都好<br />\n點知一打開兩隻雞鎚<br />\n之後我諗住行埋去counter屌鳩d m記妹<br />\n最後我都係唔敢"},{"pid":"2ced8931b5536d040f70191efe760e81c3536b92","tid":619161,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:41:37.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"10b8738073121331e06aa1b7b0157a8523f10cbb","tid":619161,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"2/10 見有圖"},{"pid":"eef0a61f5d95c2f1de9ab2cd8c08c291059e8308","tid":619161,"uid":17496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"正評係比你最後兩句咁老實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b7dae50364ee34a74829cefae5e20afa447d59","tid":619161,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"叫你老母右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ce3f593134ca0dc13e528e539fd7daf8bf8d5a","tid":619161,"uid":176111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"渣ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8a622887c1d91b23bf8949f29378c18525e8c7","tid":619161,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef0a61f5d95c2f1de9ab2c